column5: Great for plowing ice roads on your favorite lake. Must come and pick up. No shipping. P.S. bring tools for removal!!
Does it come with a truck attached?
Does it come with a truck attached?  Yep, just washed inside and out!!!
That's a good laugh for a Tuesday morning.  But, I certainly hope nobody was injured.
Is that Simcoe?  NAH, somewhere in the US. Iowa I think.
Is that Simcoe?  One only wished. Atleast it would be safe for walking.
